[h2 
	" Rules of the #tasvideos IRC channel
	$LF
]h2
[h3 
	" Freenode Policies
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"All users of #tasvideos IRC channel must adhere to 
	[a class=extlink href=https://freenode.net/policies rel=nofollow 
		"freenode.net policies
	]a
	".
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Site Rules
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	[a class=intlink href=/SiteRules 
		"Discussion board rules
	]a
	" are enforced where applicable (for example, asking for ROM links or providing them is not allowed).
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Bots
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"No speaking bots except 
	(__wikiLink|/TASVideoAgent|TASVideoAgent)
	" and BisqBot (which is 
	[a class=intlink href=/Forum/T/17899 
		"no longer around
	]a
	"). Personal bots which do nothing but logging is fine.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"No public automated messages of any other kind, including "now playing" scripts.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Operators
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Channel operation is handled mostly by 
	[tt 
		"ChanServ
	]tt
	" of Freenode. We give operator permissions to a few trusted users on a need basis.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"If there's a disturbance on the channel, don't be afraid to message operators - the following users have operator access on the IRC channel:
